<div class="about-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0891b2 0%, #06b6d4 100%); color: white; padding: 60px 0;">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">About Jan Hofmeyer Community Services</h1>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
            <div class="about-content">
                <p class="lead">
                    Jan Hofmeyer Community Services ("JHCS") is situated in Vredendorp Johannesburg. It is a non-racial charity organisation registered with the Department of Social Development as an independent non-profit organization on the 1 August 2000 (009/757/NPO), to uplift the marginalized communities of Jan Hofmeyer, Vredepark and Vredendorp. Since 20 June 2008 JHCS is also registered as a section 21 Company. The organisation is registered with SARS in terms of section 18a of the Income tax act. Donations to JHCS may in part be recovered from income tax in terms of section 18a. We are on level 4 BBEEE compliant.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

