        <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Our Story</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
                <p>Jan Hofmeyer Community Services was born from a simple but powerful vision: that every person deserves the opportunity to thrive in a supportive community. What started as a small group of dedicated volunteers has grown into a comprehensive organization serving thousands of community members across various programs.</p>
                <p>Named after Jan Hofmeyer, a champion of social justice and community development, our organization carries forward his legacy of compassionate service and unwavering commitment to human dignity.</p>
                <p>Over the past twelve years, we have evolved from providing basic assistance to developing comprehensive programs that address root causes and create sustainable solutions. Our approach focuses on empowerment, education, and community building.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

